General.Name: Canyon Resources Ltd
General.Description: Canyon Resources Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the development and exploration of bauxite properties and engineering studies in West Africa. Its flagship property is the 100% owned Minim Martap Bauxite project located in central Cameroon. The company was formerly known as Castlemaine Resources Limited and changed its name to Canyon Resources Limited in March 2010. Canyon Resources Limited was incorporated in 2009 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
